		3-1. if insertion makes frozen rows over current displayed rows, scrolling down cannot bring you more rows. Because all row displayed are frozen.
	4. how many frozen rows are removed, frozen rows decrease in same quantity.
	5. when max visible rows (columns) are less than frozen rows, frozen rows become equal to max rows (columns).
